      "review_id": "rJghfrNnKS",
      "sentence_index": 0,
      "text": "The paper studies the Bayesian inferences with the generative adversarial network (GAN).",
      "suffix": "",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rJghfrNnKS",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "text": "In the first half of the paper, the general framework of the Bayes estimation is introduced.",
      "suffix": "",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rJghfrNnKS",
      "sentence_index": 2,
      "text": "Then, The authors proposed how to incorporate GAN to the Bayesian inference.",
      "suffix": "",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rJghfrNnKS",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "text": "Some computational methods for calculating the mean of the statistic under the posterior distribution are described.",
      "suffix": "",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rJghfrNnKS",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "text": "Then, numerical experiments using MNIST and Celeb-A datasets are presented.",
      "suffix": "\n\n",
      "review_action": "arg_structuring",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-structuring_summary",
      "aspect": "none",
      "polarity": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rJghfrNnKS",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "text": "Though the Bayesian inference using GAN is a natural idea, learning algorithms proposed in this paper are simple and are not intensively developed.",
      "suffix": "",
      "review_action": "arg_evaluative",
      "fine_review_action": "none",
      "aspect": "asp_originality",
      "polarity": "pol_negative"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rJghfrNnKS",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "text": "In numerical experiments, there is no comparison with major competitors besides random sampling in the active learning setup.",
      "suffix": "",
      "review_action": "arg_evaluative",
      "fine_review_action": "none",
      "aspect": "asp_meaningful-comparison",
      "polarity": "pol_negative"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rJghfrNnKS",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "text": "Hence, the effectiveness and advantage of the proposed methods are not clear.",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_evaluative",
      "fine_review_action": "none",
      "aspect": "asp_motivation-impact",
      "polarity": "pol_negative"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "rJghfrNnKS",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "text": "- In active learning, the proposed method should be compared with other methods such as Bayesian DNN using dropout, etc.",
      "suffix": "\n",
      "review_action": "arg_request",
      "fine_review_action": "arg-request_experiment",
      "aspect": "asp_meaningful-comparison",
